1. *Dao* je svoju podršku njenim naporima. (He gave his support to her efforts.)
2. Ona je *dala* svoju mudrost prijateljima. (She gave her wisdom to her friends.)
3. Našoj porodici je *dato* mnogo ljubavi. (Our family was given a lot of love.)
4. *Dao* je nam priliku da uspemo. (He gave us the opportunity to succeed.)
5. Oni su *dali* nam nade da se izborimo sa situacijom. (They gave us hope to fight the situation.)